account.delete-account-header: Tipika password ino tanaa isip ajo iyeu nimputa akount ino.
account.delete-account-message: Tini mputa akaunt ino, mintoki arinyokino, nepoiyei lomon linono
account.delete-fail: Keeyetae ntoki naitaroiye, meiputaroi akaunt ino
account.delete-success: Eiputaru tata akaunt ino tata, mpungo tata

connection.error-retry: Ketii ntoki nataroiye, iyeu nisaan aitoki?

consent-question.answer:
I soma/aininingwa nekoni lomon lainen teeisudori teserian, kaiyelo ajo, keiyeuni nerewi lomon lainen peiye atum reto ee silingini.

Kaiyelo lutungana loodol lomon lainen.

Tenaiseiye "Atashamaie" a tengelua ajing inia reto.

Teneasei "Masham" a tengelua ajo mayeu najing inia reto.
consent-question.question:
Pi iyou ana reto lasima pii eshamaa ninkinko pii kisudoo lomon linono.

Enjere soma tanaa nining'o nikinko tini kisudoo lomon linono

create-account.introduction: Pii intibir akaunt ino Keishakino pii idip Kuna oito
create-account.username-password: Tipika ng'arn inono pooki nitibir password

enroll-in-program.introduction-information: Pii itum reto naishakino oo tengoitei naishakino, ikiyeu lomon lekimpirita

inclusion-status.creating: Ijoo iyo lomon linono laitosha pii kidol tanaa ikingeluni tijinga ana reto
inclusion-status.inclusion-status-negative: Tapaliki iyoo amu mitum ana reto. Tanaa keyatae niyeu niparu tooshoki iyoo.
inclusion-status.notify: Ikiliki iye tanaa ikitipikaki atua ana reto

login-account.incorrect-credentials: Teneitushuli ng'arn ninono pookin oo password nishooie mikiyelouni. Ngila aitoki.

registration-summary.no-validation-conclusion:
Ashe. Eedipe nkigeroto ino.

Itumu SMS/WhatsApp te namba ee simu ninjoie tangata dorop nikintodol ajo ingero.

Ikini ana kingerore ataatua mperot tomon ongwan tanaa impaulua.

Ele nkilikwai le mwisho tanakata.
